<item>
            <title>[LU-15939] configure script changes system header and config files</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15939</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Configure script changes system header and config files:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;/usr/src/linux-headers-$(uname -r)/include/generated/autoconf.h&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;/usr/src/linux-headers-$(uname -r)/include/config/auto.conf&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And as a result we hit the following error while loading Lustre client modules:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
# modprobe lustre
modprobe: ERROR: could not insert &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;lustre&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: Exec format error

kernel: [187850.110155] module: x86/modules: Skipping invalid relocation target, existing value is nonzero &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; type 1, loc 00000000cab2976e, val ffffffffc110f9f8
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
